******************************
* Backup and Disaster Recovery
******************************

* Recover data from snapshot

* Select snapshot 

* select action tab

* Creat volume from snapshot

* Attach it to a EC2 instance

* Connect to the EC2 instance

* Take control

* Check whether volume is attached
# sudo lsblk

* Chek if there is any data on volume
# sudo file -s /dev/xvdf

* Mount HDD
# sudo mount /dev/xvdf /fileserver

# cd /fileserver

* Check whether your backup done or not
# ls


